{"id": "1261366215637602314", "channel_id": "1261366215637602314", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "跟之前比交换了一下顺序，让凯刻斯去打宁菲亚了，大致配队没有差异\n全常驻当然不是最佳攻略，持续更新是为了让大家知道数值还在无限定能达到全奖的区间，有在努力捞超限全常驻了，也许全部70，80的就能375呢，视频全流程B站都有，限定用完了的可以看看怎么凑队伍。（其实我第一天就打完了只是一直没上DC最近）", "timestamp": "2024-07-12T16:59:00.859000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1261366216006697040", "filename": "Screenshot_20240709_005934_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 204951, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1261366215637602314/1261366216006697040/Screenshot_20240709_005934_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfd54&is=69caabd4&hm=e845a4cb2cf6693ad55dd90155b975207da5ace161d195bda721870a2cefbe58&"}, {"id": "1261366216321142927", "filename": "Screenshot_20240708_235324_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 203157, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1261366215637602314/1261366216321142927/Screenshot_20240708_235324_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfd55&is=69caabd5&hm=45864cfecff8585ba6683368f1ddaf0e5e7d884749a2203620097824d585ee58&"}, {"id": "1261366216732311552", "filename": "Screenshot_20240708_225722_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 208598, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1261366215637602314/1261366216732311552/Screenshot_20240708_225722_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfd55&is=69caabd5&hm=df92cfe4bf90e7db6ee85060888608ca30fbebb9d83b7db81ffde9f5d1eb2035&"}, {"id": "1261366217088700480", "filename": "Screenshot_20240708_232924_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 210518, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1261366215637602314/1261366217088700480/Screenshot_20240708_232924_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfd55&is=69caabd5&hm=a4f705ad26e29b3